    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an intern who left something behind at the office and needs to come get it at night, but when you get out of the elevator, something feels a little off. In this first-person atmospheric horror game, discover the Paragon Corporation office and the secrets it holds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETURN TO OFFICE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/ea1840e73fe4e58190d74a32780a25f5.poster.avif?t=1757888592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/ea1840e73fe4e58190d74a32780a25f5.webm?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/ea1840e73fe4e58190d74a32780a25f5.mp4?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Paragon Tower, home of the Paragon Corporation, welcomes you for an after-hours visit. The constant buzz of fluorescent lights. The scent of mildewing carpet. What's not to love?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INVESTIGATE THE DELIVERABLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/d87184c24c681318949078a0df0851b0.poster.avif?t=1757888592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/d87184c24c681318949078a0df0851b0.webm?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/d87184c24c681318949078a0df0851b0.mp4?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect notes and solve puzzles to uncover lore and progress further into the lower levels of the office.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CLOCK OUT, IF YOU CAN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/6e65ea81f8c3d052be5fa604c5868a9e.poster.avif?t=1757888592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/6e65ea81f8c3d052be5fa604c5868a9e.webm?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314670/extras/6e65ea81f8c3d052be5fa604c5868a9e.mp4?t=1757888592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something may be lurking in the shadows of Paragon Corporation. To avoid getting caught, you might need to be careful.</p>",
